         NO-PATH-VECTOR TLV.";
      reference
        "RFC 8685: Path Computation Element Communication Protocol
                   (PCEP) Extensions for the Hierarchical Path
                   Computation Element (H-PCE) Architecture

         https://www.iana.org/assignments/pcep
         /pcep.xhtml#no-path-vector-tlv";
    }

